---

<Layout title="Velocity7">



  <ContainerFW>

    <SectionEmail>
      <Fragment slot="title">
        Our Conversion-Focused, High Performance Theme.
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="desc">
        The perfect balance between website template and custom code. Created to rapidly build successful websites for Australian businesses.
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="cover">
        <Picture
                  src={Pagecover}
                  sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 2000px, 1000px"
                  widths={[1000, 1500, 2000]}
                  aspectRatio="3:2"
                  background="#f2f2f2"
                  fit="cover"
                  position="center"
                  class="w-full rounded duration-200 hover:shadow-sm"
                />
      </Fragment>
    </SectionEmail>

  </ContainerFW>

  <ContainerFW>
    <FeaturesFW />
  </ContainerFW>

  <ContainerXL>
    <SectionExplain>
      <Fragment slot="title">
        Crush your Competition with Ease.
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="desc">
        Are you looking at competitors around you with beautiful custom websites that are stealing your customers with ease? If so, Velocity is for you.
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="cover">
        <Picture
                  src={PagecoverSecondary}
                  sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 2000px, 1000px"
                  widths={[1000, 1500, 2000]}
                  aspectRatio="3:2"
                  background="#f2f2f2"
                  fit="cover"
                  position="center"
                  class="w-full rounded duration-200 hover:shadow-sm"
                />
      </Fragment>
    </SectionExplain>
  </ContainerXL>

  <ContainerXL>
    <SectionTextarea>
      <Fragment slot="title">Making Business Simpler.</Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="desc" class="max-w-6xl">
        Velocity is the website framework that brings speed, functionality, and flexibility all into one, developed over 5 years with these 3 points in mind. Intuitive well-designed components that can be quickly rebranded. Velocity empowers developers to build high-performing websites with ease. Create websites that can grow with the demands of your business. With Velocity, you can unlock the full potential of your business and deliver exceptional service and experiences to your customer.
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="cover">
        <Picture
                  src={CoverTextarea}
                  sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 2000px, 1000px"
                  widths={[1000, 1500, 2000]}
                  aspectRatio="3:2"
                  background="#f2f2f2"
                  fit="cover"
                  position="center"
                  class="w-full rounded duration-200 hover:shadow-sm"
                />
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="iconleft">
        <Icon class="w-16 h-16" name="simple-icons:zapier" />
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="textleft">
        Integrate Velocity7 seamlessly into your workflows with Zapier's powerful automation platform. Connect Velocity7 to your favorite apps and streamline your processes effortlessly. With Zapier's extensive library of triggers and actions, you can automate tasks, synchronize data, and trigger events in Velocity7 with just a few clicks. Boost your productivity and efficiency by harnessing the full potential of Velocity7 through Zapier's intuitive interface.
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="iconright">
        <Icon class="w-16 h-16" name="simple-icons:netlify" />
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="textright">
        Unlock the true potential of your website by integrating Velocity7 using Netlify's robust API capabilities. Seamlessly incorporate Velocity7 into your web development workflow and enhance your website's performance. With Netlify's simple and flexible API, you can easily access Velocity7's features and leverage its power to create dynamic, personalized experiences for your users. Take control of your website's velocity and elevate your online presence with the seamless integration of Velocity7 through Netlify's API.
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="iconleft2">
        <Icon class="w-16 h-16" name="simple-icons:googleads" />
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="textleft2">
        Maximize your advertising effectiveness with Google Ads' built-in conversion tracking. Easily track and measure the success of your campaigns by monitoring the conversions that matter most to your business. Gain valuable insights into customer behavior and optimize your ad strategy accordingly. With Google Ads' comprehensive conversion tracking, you can make data-driven decisions and drive higher ROI for your advertising efforts.
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="iconright2">
        <Icon class="w-16 h-16" name="simple-icons:stripe" />
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="textright2">
        Streamline your payment process and boost sales with Stripe's secure payment gateway. With one-click checkout, you can provide a seamless payment experience for your customers, reducing cart abandonment and driving conversions. Benefit from Stripe's cost-effective rates, transparent pricing, and robust fraud prevention tools. Whether you're selling products, services, or subscriptions, Stripe empowers you to handle payments with confidence while delivering a frictionless payment experience.
      </Fragment>      
    </SectionTextarea>
  </ContainerXL>

  <ContainerXL>
    <SectionExplain>
      <Fragment slot="title">
        Crush your Competition with Ease.
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="desc">
        When it comes to website frameworks, Velocity stands out as a top choice for developers seeking a powerful and versatile solution. With Velocity, you can harness the latest web technologies and best practices to create websites that are not only visually stunning but also highly functional and performant. Its modular structure promotes code reusability, reducing development time and effort. Velocity's extensive documentation and active community support ensure that developers have access to the resources they need to overcome challenges and explore new possibilities. Whether you're building a personal blog or a complex web application, Velocity empowers you to create exceptional online experiences that captivate and engage your audience. With its solid foundation and continuous updates, Velocity remains at the forefront of website frameworks, driving innovation and enabling developers to bring their ideas to fruition.
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="cover">
        <Picture
                  src={PagecoverThird}
                  sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 2000px, 1000px"
                  widths={[1000, 1500, 2000]}
                  aspectRatio="3:2"
                  background="#f2f2f2"
                  fit="cover"
                  position="center"
                  class="w-full rounded duration-200 hover:shadow-sm"
                />
      </Fragment>
    </SectionExplain>
  </ContainerXL>

  <Container>

      <Sectionhead>
        <Fragment slot="title">Light as a Feather.</Fragment>
        <Fragment slot="desc" class="max-w-4xl"
          >We've spent 5 years developing Velocity into the one of the fastest website foundations available. 
          V7 comes in at a feather-weight 68kb pageload for a full website ready for rapid branding, infinitly extendable.
        </Fragment>
      </Sectionhead>

      <Integrations />

  </Container>

  <ContainerFW>
    <GallerySlider />
  </ContainerFW>

  <Container>

      <Sectionhead>
        <Fragment slot="title">Turn Around in 21 Days.</Fragment>
        <Fragment slot="desc">
          All components are styled to your brand and pages duplicated from your old site by our team during initial deployment. 
          Watch our development live on the fly to help us move faster or use your multiple design revisions.
        </Fragment>
      </Sectionhead>

      <Logos />

  </Container>

  <Container>
    <Sectionhead>
      <Fragment slot="title">Ready to Launch?</Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="desc" class="max-w-4xl">
        With a size for every business, we're here to help!
      </Fragment>
    </Sectionhead>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-10 mx-auto mt-12">
      {pricing.map((item) => <Pricing plan={item} />)}
    </div>
  </Container>
  
</Layout>
